                "invention-title": [
                    "Tangential combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor",
                    "一种切向燃烧式沼气重整制氢反应器"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a tangential combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor. The tangential combustion type methane reforming hydrogen production reactor comprises a reactor shell, a combustor and a plurality of reaction tubes, the reactor shell is provided with a reactor accommodating cavity, and the upper part of the reactor shell is also provided with a flue gas outlet communicated with the reactor accommodating cavity; a part of the plurality of reaction tubes are inserted into the reactor accommodating cavity, the combustor is arranged on the side surface of the reactor shell, a combustion tube is arranged at an outlet of a gas mixing cavity of the combustor, the combustion tube is communicated with the reactor accommodating cavity, a flow guide plate arranged in the reactor shell is arranged at an outlet of the combustion tube, and the flow guide plate extends to the flue gas outlet. The combustor is arranged at the tangential position of the bottom of the reactor shell, flue gas generated by combustion preheats raw material gas sent to the bottom of the reaction pipe from the gas inlet pipe, the heat exchange efficiency is high, then the flue gas spirally and upwards flows from the bottom of the reactor under the action of the flow guide plate and exchanges heat with the reaction pipe, and the energy utilization efficiency is further improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种切向燃烧式沼气重整制氢反应器，包括：反应器壳体、燃烧器和若干反应管；反应器壳体具有反应器容纳腔，反应器壳体的上部还设有与反应器容纳腔连通的烟气出口；若干反应管的一部分插置于反应器容纳腔内，燃烧器设置于反应器壳体的侧面，燃烧器的气体混合腔出口设置燃烧管，燃烧管与反应器容纳腔连通，燃烧管出口处设置有内置于反应器壳体内部的导流板，导流板延伸至烟气出口。本发明在反应器壳体底部切向位置布置燃烧器，燃烧产生的烟气预先加热由进气管送至反应管底部的原料气，换热效率高，随之在导流板的作用下从反应器底部螺旋向上流动，并与反应管进行换热，进一步提高能量利用效率。"
                }
            ]
